&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Here’s a summary of the role:&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Diligent is seeking an experienced &lt;strong&gt;Client Success Advisor&lt;/strong&gt; to join our growing Customer Success team, partnering with key accounts across Australia and New Zealand to drive meaningful adoption, retention, and long-term customer value across our GRC platform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a role for someone who thrives on impact and focuses on enabling real outcomes through the intersection of people, process, and technology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Diligent,&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Client Success Advisors&lt;/strong&gt; are at the heart of our retention strategy. You’ll work closely with clients to unlock value, strengthen engagement, and ensure they are truly successful in how they manage governance, risk, and compliance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re driven by meaningful client impact, love solving complex business challenges, and want to help organisations operate with confidence — this is your next move.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Here’s a breakdown of what you’ll do (not all of it, just the important stuff):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with key clients across Australia &amp;amp; New Zealand to understand how they’re using the platform, identify gaps, and drive greater value and adoption&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a trusted advisor, delivering best-practice guidance to help customers improve risk, audit, and compliance outcomes using the platform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain structured account plans, proactively tracking engagement, usage trends, and overall customer health&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify at-risk accounts early (low usage, disengagement, or operational challenges) and take targeted action to re-engage and improve outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with Sales, Product, and Support teams to resolve issues, influence enhancements, and support expansion opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage a portfolio of accounts, prioritising activity based on customer need, urgency, and potential impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
